Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 07:32:19 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 01/13] Add Zig Content Shell: C boundary proof
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A shim so thin it's barely there,
dlsym finds ContentMain with care.
Three subclasses, one override chain—
Google loads, the proof is plain.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
